{"tid":1613091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"將印尼爆眼新聞推到印尼","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:40:40.000Z","uid":321625,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a5732ca2acb54ee7863a9ff8a8047cc6f562a7","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"一名本地印尼語傳媒SUARA女記者Veby Mega Indah在灣仔站行人天橋直播採訪時，懷疑被數米外的警員擎槍射中，橡膠子彈傷及右眼眼眉位置倒地，直至今日確定永永久性失明。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>懇請各位連登巴打請將呢單新聞推到東南亞，令佢哋知道黑警謀殺記者，危害所有公民亦安全。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n印尼的國民多用Facebook作主語社交媒體<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e97beae79cd0c4cdd0706134a888cd31174bb4","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"7674d4922476cd3d20f1c14536eab9d4063b2670","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"14d4263653c123dedf52e19417e02f85f12ec22a","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"a0bbd2cce4ee563efe67eed262aa648fd41974ce","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:31:59.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"64a68c7e1ca32aa954d6ac543c1d16c551d0f374","tid":1613091,"uid":321625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"432a308de1f79804f45e9d2ae42dfbf12121959d","tid":1613091,"uid":19482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:34:48.000Z","msg":"如果屋企有印傭既 叫佢地同家鄉既親戚spread開去 仲有叫佢地用印尼文寫一篇報導 係印尼報紙登報！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輸出革命！！</span>"},{"pid":"9bc039f128accddc0f89377aa4e59c97face8d41","tid":1613091,"uid":32162